metadata.name: Underneath the mist⁣
metadata.description:
Underneath the mist, a lake lies hidden. She skillfully is concealing her beauty, under the cover of her own evaporating water.⁣
⁣
Finally a moment to rest from the staring eyes of admiration. A moment of silence, peace and tranquility.⁣
⁣
If you close your eyes, you will hear the gentle touch of the lake and the shore. An unbroken bond that lasts forever.⁣
